    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the creamy base mixture with your<strong> salmon flakes</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until the pastry is golden and crisp and the edges have puffed up – this is your <strong>flaked</strong> <strong>salmon tart</strong></p>",
