    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>salad </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>balsamic dressing </strong>and gently toss it all together – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
